{"title":"Wizard Works UltraGrid Collection","link":"https://theradavist.com/wizard-works-ultragrid-collection/","date":1746444651000,"content":"<p><em>The ultimate retro tech fabric, UltraGrid, is now available as a mini collection of summer favorites by London bag maker <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/wizard-works/\" target=\"_blank\">Wizard Works</a>…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_UltraGrid_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_UltraGrid_02.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_UltraGrid_02.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_UltraGrid_02.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The collection is available in two colorways, Black and Avocado, and consists of two of Wizard Works’ most popular bags, Lil Presto Barrel Bag and Teeny Houdini Saddle Bag, and introducing a new product to Wizard Works, retro-inspired, Triangle Frame Bag.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_wbg_Ultragrid_Triangle_Frame_Bag_Avocado.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_wbg_Ultragrid_Triangle_Frame_Bag_Avocado.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_wbg_Ultragrid_Triangle_Frame_Bag_Avocado.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_wbg_Ultragrid_Triangle_Frame_Bag_Avocado.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_wbg_Ultragrid_Triangle_Frame_Bag_Black.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_wbg_Ultragrid_Triangle_Frame_Bag_Black.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_wbg_Ultragrid_Triangle_Frame_Bag_Black.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_wbg_Ultragrid_Triangle_Frame_Bag_Black.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The Triangle Frame Bag features elastic lacing, as per the other frame bags in the Wizard Works range, a slick RiRi chunky zip, and a 1.5L snack-holding capacity. It is available in two angles (78° and 82°) that refer to the angle between the seat tube and top tube.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Lil_Presto_Small_Avocado.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Lil_Presto_Small_Avocado.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Lil_Presto_Small_Avocado.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Lil_Presto_Small_Avocado.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Lil_Presto_Large_Black.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Lil_Presto_Large_Black.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Lil_Presto_Large_Black.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Lil_Presto_Large_Black.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The hardshell Lil Presto Barrel Bag is a great day ride companion and is available in two sizes (1.8L and 3.4L). The Teeny Houdini Saddle Bag (one size) is the perfect bag for snugging away a tube and tools. The UltraGrid Collection looks great as a set or equally as awesome as standalone bags.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Teeny_Houdini_Black.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Teeny_Houdini_Black.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Teeny_Houdini_Black.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Teeny_Houdini_Black.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Teeny_Houdini_Avocado.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Teeny_Houdini_Avocado.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Teeny_Houdini_Avocado.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_WBG_Ultragrid_Teeny_Houdini_Avocado.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Not just for looks, beneath its cool aesthetic, UltraGrid is an environmentally friendly, technical-performing fabric. UltraGrid is woven at a Bluesign-approved facility with 210d recycled nylon yarn from pre-consumer industrial waste. A double 200d Ultra grid provides exceptional tear-strength and visual impact. UltraGrid has a C0 DWR coating, free from toxic PFCs, and is finished with a waterproof PU backing.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_UltraGrid_03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_UltraGrid_03.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_UltraGrid_03.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/05/Wizard_Works_UltraGrid_03.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Wizard Works has also selected four of their favorite shades of UltraGrid: Avocado, Berry, Coyote, and Black, which are now available to add to any of their custom bags.</p>\n<p>See the whole lot at <a href=\"https://www.wizard.works/product-category/ultragrid-collection/\" target=\"_blank\">Wizard Works</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/wizard-works-ultragrid-collection/\">Wizard Works UltraGrid Collection</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"538250c155bed32f000ca152f28cf401fbccb9bf30f96031d5ed069d70240ee8","category":"Cycling"}